main event: A UFO sighting was reported in West Nyark, New York on July 24, 1958.
interesting points: The sighting lasted between 3-10 seconds., The object was observed moving from East to West and had a vapor trail., It appeared to be above the observer and had an elliptical shape., The report concluded that the sighting was likely a meteor., There were no photographs attached to the report.
sighted object: one object with a vapor trail
witness description: observer above who reported the sighting
